Cyberpunk style: A towering crystalline structure at the center of a neon-drenched cityscape, with countless glowing data streams flowing from different directions—some from sleek corporate monoliths, others from chaotic street-level nodes, and ethereal threads descending from the cloud-covered sky above. Each stream is a different electric color (cyan, magenta, gold, green) representing different identity sources converging into the central crystal, which refracts and transforms them into a single unified beam shooting upward. Silhouettes of people walking on elevated walkways below appear as dark figures with subtle holographic auras around them, each aura a unique pattern. Rain falls through the scene, catching the neon light. The atmosphere is misty with digital particles floating like fireflies. The perspective is looking up from street level toward the towering identity nexus, creating a sense of scale and technological complexity. Dark purple and deep blue dominate the shadows while electric highlights cut through the urban fog.
